jay arlen jones is an american film and television actor , active since the early 1980s . his most recognized role is that of occam , the african-american slave enlisted as a patriot fighter by his master , in the revolutionary war epic the patriot ( 2000 ) . after portraying leon in eight legged freaks ( 2001 ) , he participated in the short film nines and the television film the least among you ( 2009 ) , but has not appeared onscreen since .